#. Tag: title
#: guides.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detailed Guides"
msgstr "Detaljni vodiči"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "This chapter describes how to perform some common tasks in &stage;."
msgstr "Ovo poglavlje opisuje kako izvesti neke uobičajene zadatke u &stage;."

#. Tag: title
#: guides.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a &HTML; Slideshow"
msgstr "Napravite &HTML; prezentaciju"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Turn an existing presentation into standard &HTML; pages with accompanying "
"navigation aids."
msgstr ""
"Pretvorite postojeću prezentaciju u standardnu &HTML; stranicu sa "
"pripadajućim navigacijskim pomagalima."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First, either make a new presentation, or open an existing one. Then, click "
"on <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guimenuitem>Export as HTML...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>"
msgstr ""
"Prvo, ili napravite novu prezentaciju, ili otvorite postojeću. Onda, "
"kliknite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izvedi kao "
"HTML...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "You will then get a dialog box asking for a few details:"
msgstr "Dobit ćete tada dialog izbornik koji pita za par detalja:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: guides.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Fill in the details for your &HTML; slideshow</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Ispunite detalje za svoju &HTML; prezentaciju</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: guides.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Fill in the details for your &HTML; slideshow</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Ispunite detalje za svoju &HTML; prezentaciju</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fill in <guilabel>Title</guilabel> and <guilabel>Author</guilabel> fields. "
"Select the slides which should be exported. If you want to change a name "
"used on the &HTML; page for each slide double click on the name and edit it "
"inline."
msgstr ""
"Ispunite <guilabel>Naziv</guilabel> i <guilabel>Autor</guilabel> polja. "
"Odaberite slajdove koji bi trebali biti izvezeni. Ako želite promijeniti ime "
"korišteno na &HTML; stranici za svaki slajd pritisnite dvostruki klik na "
"naziv i urediti ga u redu."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>Output preview</guilabel> area the downsized slides are "
"displayed and you can check the correct slide order and browse the "
"presentation with the <guiicon>&lt;</guiicon> and <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> "
"buttons."
msgstr ""
"U <guilabel>Izlaznom prikazu</guilabel> područja su smanjeni slajdovi "
"prikazani i vi možete provjeriti tačan redoslijed slajdova i pregledati "
"prezentaciju sa <guiicon>&lt;</guiicon> i <guiicon>&gt;</guiicon> dugmadima."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Now you can select a stylesheet with the configuration of the &HTML; options."
msgstr "Sada možete označiti stil sa konfiguracijom &HTML; opcija."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To actually produce your &HTML; presentation, press the <guibutton>Export</"
"guibutton> button and select a folder."
msgstr ""
"Da zapravo proizvedete vašu &HTML; prezenaciju, pritisnite <guibutton>Izvoz</"
"guibutton> dugme i označite folder."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"What we now have are the newly-produced <filename>html/</filename> and "
"<filename>pics/</filename> folders, created where we earlier set the path:"
msgstr ""
"Ono štp sad imamo su novo-napravljeni <filename>html/</filename> i "
"<filename>pics/</filename> folderi, kreirani kada smo prije postavili ovu "
"putanju:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: guides.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The newly created &HTML; slideshow folders</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Novi kreirani &HTML; prezentacija folderi</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: guides.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The newly created &HTML; slideshow folders</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Novi kreirani &HTML; prezentacija folderi</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There is also an <filename>index.html</filename> file to launch your web "
"slideshow."
msgstr ""
"Postoji i <filename>index.html</filename> datoteka za pokretanje vaše web "
"prezentacije."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can see how it works by using your file manager or web browser to open "
"the <filename>index.html</filename> file. Click where prompted, and the "
"first slide of your presentation is displayed. It will now behave as a "
"&stage; slideshow."
msgstr ""
"Možete vidjeti kako radi pomoću upravitelja datoteka ili web preglednika za "
"otvaranje <filename>index.html</filename> datoteke. Kliknite gdje je "
"zatraženo, i prikazan je prvi slajd vaše prezentacije. Sada će se ponašati "
"kao &stage; prezentacija."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each click on the arrow icons take you to the next or previous slide. To get "
"back to the start of the slideshow click on the slide icon."
msgstr ""
"Svaki klik na ikonu strelice vas vodi na prethodni ili sljedeći slajd. Da "
"biste se vratili na početak prezentacije kliknite na ikonu slajda."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To share your presentation with the world, transfer the newly-produced files "
"to a network-accessible location (&ie; webspace), remembering to keep the "
"folder structure intact."
msgstr ""
"Da biste podijelili prezentaciju sa svijetom, prenesite novo-napravljene "
"datoteke u mrežno-pristupačnu lokaciju (&ie; webspace), imajući na umu da "
"zadržite strukturu foldera netakutu."

#. Tag: title
#: guides.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating &stage; Templates"
msgstr "Kreiranje &stage; Šablona"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "It is very easy to create a new template for &stage;."
msgstr "Veoma je lako kreirati novi šablon za &stage;."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have made a presentation in a style that you would like to use again, "
"you can save it as a template."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste napravili prezentaciju u stilu koji biste željeli opet koristiti, "
"možete ga spasiti kao šablon."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid "This tutorial will show how we can make a new template and save it."
msgstr ""
"Ovaj tutorijal će vam pokazati kako pravimo novi šablon i spašavamo ga."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open &stage; and create a new document."
msgstr "Otvorite &stage; i kreirajte novi dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To add a little sparkle to the blank slide, we can change the slide "
"background - do this by selecting the <guilabel>Document background</"
"guilabel> tool in the Tools docker."
msgstr ""
"Da biste dodali malo živosti na prazan slajd, možemo promijeniti pozadinu "
"slajda - ovo uradite odabirom <guilabel>Pozadina dokumenta</guilabel> alatke "
"u Doku alatki."

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"We want the background to look attractive, so you may choose to use an image "
"as a background by clicking the <guibutton>Set image</guibutton> button: "
"feel free to experiment, but keep it beautiful!"
msgstr ""
"Želimo da pozadina izgleda atraktivno, tako da možete odabrati sliku za "
"pozadinu klikom na <guibutton>Postavi sliku</guibutton> dugme: osjećajte se "
"slobodnim da eksperimentišete, ali neka ostane lijepo!"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: guides.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Choosing a slide background</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Biranje pozadine slajda</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: guides.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Choosing a slide background</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Biranje pozadine slajda</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The page should now have the background you desire. Create a text box, and "
"type a heading for your slide:"
msgstr ""
"Stranica bi sad trebala imati pozadinu koju vi želite. Kreirajte okvir za "
"tekst, i pišite naslov za vaš slajd:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: guides.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding a Heading to the new template</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Dodavanje naslova za novi šablon</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: guides.docbook:158
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding a Heading to the new template</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Dodavanje naslova za novi šablon</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: guides.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are happy with your template, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Save As</guimenuitem></menuchoice> and select "
"<guilabel>Opendocument Presentation Template</guilabel> filetype in the file "
"dialog."
msgstr ""
"Kada ste zadovoljni sa šablonom, idite na <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Snimi kao</guimenuitem></menuchoice> i označite "
"<guilabel>Otvori dokument šablona prezetacija</guilabel> tip datoteke u "
"dijalog datoteke."
